The '''[[Exchange]] [[Utility belt/Legends|utility belt]]''' was a special utility belt manufactured and distributed by the Exchange in the period following the [[Jedi Civil War]]. Although it was stated to be used primarily by mechanics, its tools aided in less honorable tasks as well.

